data.Description: Baga Beach is one of the most popular and vibrant beaches in North Goa, known for its lively atmosphere, golden sandy shores, and exciting nightlife. It is located close to Calangute Beach and is a favorite destination for tourists looking for adventure, relaxation, and entertainment.
